---

<Layout 
  title={pageTitle}
  description={pageDescription}
  keywords={pageKeywords}
  pageType="website"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#D3E4FD] via-white to-[#FFDEE2] opacity-90"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-20 left-10 w-96 h-96 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400/20 to-teal-400/20 rounded-full morph-blob blur-3xl"></div>
    
    <div class="container-custom relative z-10">
      <nav class="mb-6">
        <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-salon-darkblue">Home</a></li>
          <li class="text-gray-400">/</li>
          <li><a href="/locations" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-salon-darkblue">Locations</a></li>
          <li class="text-gray-400">/</li>
          <li class="text-gray-900 font-medium">Wainui</li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
      
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
          <span class="gradient-text">Wainui</span> Village Hair Specialists
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
          Professional hair care designed for Wainui's village lifestyle. Located 20 minutes away in Kaukapakapa, Hair By Melissa specializes in natural treatments that protect against environmental factors, UV damage, and humidity.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/booking" class="btn-primary inline-flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
            Book Your Appointment
          </a>
          <a href="#village-services" class="bg-white text-gray-800 font-medium py-3 px-6 rounded-md shadow hover:shadow-lg transition inline-flex items-center justify-center">
            Village Hair Services
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Wainui Village Lifestyle -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Hair Care for Wainui's Unique Village Environment</h2>
        
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700">
          <p class="text-xl mb-6">
            Wainui represents the charm of New Zealand's rural village lifestyle - a peaceful rural community where life moves with the natural rhythms of the seasons. This beautiful location in rural Auckland presents unique opportunities for hair care that celebrates the natural beauty and active lifestyle of village living.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Understanding Wainui's Rural Climate</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Positioned in rural Auckland, Wainui experiences the natural beauty of countryside living. The community sits in a peaceful valley, creating a unique environment where fresh air, natural UV exposure, and seasonal humidity variations provide the perfect backdrop for healthy hair that thrives with proper care and attention.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-6">
            The natural rural environment offers clean air and outdoor activities that promote healthy living. This active village lifestyle enhances natural hair health when combined with proper professional care - creating vibrant, resilient hair that reflects the vitality of country living.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-6">
            Wainui's elevation and rural topography create gentle temperature variations throughout the day. Morning country air gives way to warm afternoon sun, while evening breezes bring refreshing humidity changes. These natural environmental shifts can enhance hair health when properly supported with appropriate protective treatments.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">The Active Village Community's Hair Care Needs</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Wainui is renowned for its active, outdoor-loving community, attracting residents who embrace the rural lifestyle year-round. The village community faces particular hair care opportunities that we understand and enhance through specialized treatments. Regular outdoor activities and fresh air exposure enhance natural hair vitality when supported with proper professional care.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-6">
            Many Wainui residents enjoy outdoor activities multiple times per week, from hiking to gardening to rural pursuits. This active village lifestyle benefits from professional hair care routines that enhance natural beauty. Our keratin treatments have become incredibly popular with the village community because they provide protection and manageability while maintaining hair's natural flexibility and movement.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-6">
            The active village lifestyle influences styling preferences. Wainui residents often prefer versatile styles that look great for both everyday activities and special occasions, can withstand active pursuits, and work beautifully with natural textures. Our cutting techniques celebrate these lifestyle factors, creating styles that enhance rather than compete with the natural beauty that village living encourages.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Seasonal Variations in Wainui</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            <strong>Summer (December-February):</strong> Wainui summers are vibrant, with abundant sunshine perfect for outdoor village activities. The combination of lush vegetation in the valley and fresh country air creates a wonderful environment that enhances natural hair vitality. This is our busiest season for UV protection treatments and color refresh services to complement the active summer lifestyle.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-6">
            <strong>Autumn (March-May):</strong> The changing season brings beautiful rural colors and perfect weather for outdoor pursuits. Autumn in Wainui is characterized by crisp, clear days that are ideal for exploring the countryside. This season sees increased demand for deep conditioning treatments and protective styling services to maintain hair health during active autumn months.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-6">
            <strong>Winter (June-August):</strong> While winter brings cozy village charm, the season also provides opportunities for hair restoration and renewal. Cooler temperatures and indoor gathering times make this an ideal period for intensive repair treatments and color services that will showcase beautifully when warmer weather returns.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-6">
            <strong>Spring (September-November):</strong> Spring brings renewal and often requests for lighter, fresh colors in preparation for the active outdoor season. The variable weather patterns of spring in Wainui - from peaceful mornings to refreshing afternoons - make this a perfect time for treatments that provide flexibility and protection for the coming active season.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">The Wainui Community Character</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Wainui's close-knit village population creates a wonderful community where authenticity and natural beauty are highly valued. This philosophy extends to hair care preferences, with many residents favoring styles that enhance their natural texture rather than fighting against it. The community's appreciation for sustainable, natural living also influences treatment choices, with many clients preferring services that maintain hair health and celebrate natural beauty.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-6">
            The community includes a mix of long-term residents who have deep connections to the rural lifestyle, alongside newcomers drawn by the village charm and natural beauty. This diversity creates wonderful styling opportunities as we work to honor both traditional preferences and contemporary trends, always keeping the practical demands of active village living in mind.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Access and Convenience from Wainui</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            The journey from Wainui to our Kaukapakapa salon, while requiring a 20-minute drive, offers several advantages that our clients have come to appreciate. The route through scenic rural countryside allows for a relaxing transition that prepares you for your salon experience. This peaceful journey enhances the overall effectiveness of your visit.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-6">
            Many Wainui clients use their salon appointments as part of a broader self-care routine that includes shopping in Kumeu, visiting other rural businesses, or simply enjoying the scenic drive through some of Auckland's most beautiful countryside. The appointment becomes part of a day trip that provides a welcome break from daily routines and celebrates rural living.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-6">
            Our location in Kaukapakapa provides an ideal environment for hair treatments. The peaceful rural location ensures optimal conditions for chemical processes, while the tranquil setting creates a relaxing atmosphere that many clients find superior to busier urban salon environments.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Specialized Knowledge for Village Hair Care</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Understanding Wainui's unique village environment allows us to provide superior service to our clients from this area. We know that rural living has specific hair care needs that differ from urban environments. Our professional approach ensures your hair looks and feels its best while supporting your active village lifestyle.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-6">
            We also understand that color services need to account for natural UV exposure and outdoor activities. Our color formulations and application techniques are optimized for clients who enjoy active outdoor lifestyles. This attention to lifestyle factors ensures longer-lasting, more vibrant results that enhance your natural beauty.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-6">
            Our treatment recommendations are based on years of working with rural residents and understanding how different hair types thrive in village environments. We can predict which treatments will work best for specific lifestyles and provide maintenance routines that fit realistically into the rhythm of village life.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Beach-Specific Services -->
  <section id="village-services" class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Specialized Services for Village Living</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 text-center mb-12">
          Treatments specifically designed to protect and enhance hair for active village lifestyles, UV exposure, and rural environments.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          {wainuiServices.map((service) => (
            <div class={`bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 ${service.popular ? 'border-2 border-blue-400' : ''}`}>
              {service.popular && (
                <div class="mb-4">
                  <span class="bg-blue-400 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">
                    🏡 Village Favorite
                  </span>
                </div>
              )}
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">{service.name}</h3>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
                <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-salon-darkblue">{service.price}</span>
                <span class="text-gray-600">{service.duration}</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">{service.description}</p>
              <div class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg mb-6">
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">Village Benefit:</h4>
                <p class="text-blue-700 text-sm">{service.villageBenefit}</p>
              </div>
              <a 
                href={`/services/${service.name.toLowerCase().replace(/[^a-z0-9]+/g, '-').replace(/-+/g, '-').replace(/^-|-$/g, '')}`}
                class="inline-flex items-center text-salon-darkblue font-medium hover:underline"
              >
                Learn more about {service.name}
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Beach Hair Care Tips -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Professional Village Hair Care Tips for Wainui Residents</h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
          {villageHairTips.map((tip) => (
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-teal-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-blue-200">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-blue-800">{tip.season} Care</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3 font-medium">{tip.tip}</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm italic">{tip.reason}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#D3E4FD] to-[#FFDEE2] p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800">Daily Village Hair Routine for Wainui Residents</h3>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-bold mb-3 text-salon-darkblue">Before Outdoor Activities</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm">
                <li>• Apply UV protection spray</li>
                <li>• Hydrate with leave-in conditioner</li>
                <li>• Style for active pursuits</li>
                <li>• Protect from wind exposure</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-bold mb-3 text-salon-darkblue">During Activities</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm">
                <li>• Stay hydrated for healthy hair</li>
                <li>• Keep hair covered in strong wind</li>
                <li>• Avoid excessive touching</li>
                <li>• Reapply protection products</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-bold mb-3 text-salon-darkblue">After Active Day</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm">
                <li>• Gentle cleansing as needed</li>
                <li>• Moisturizing treatment</li>
                <li>• Deep conditioning care</li>
                <li>• Air dry when possible</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Travel Information for Wainui -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Getting Here from Wainui</h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-salon-darkblue">Journey Details</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="font-medium">Distance:</span>
                <span>20 minutes</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="font-medium">Route:</span>
                <span>Wainui Road → SH16</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="font-medium">Traffic:</span>
                <span>Light rural roads</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="font-medium">Parking:</span>
                <span>Free on-site</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-salon-darkblue">Route Directions</h3>
            <ol class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex">
                <span class="bg-blue-400 text-white rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold mr-3 mt-1">1</span>
                <span>Head east on Wainui Road from village</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex">
                <span class="bg-blue-400 text-white rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold mr-3 mt-1">2</span>
                <span>Continue to SH16 intersection</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex">
                <span class="bg-blue-400 text-white rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold mr-3 mt-1">3</span>
                <span>Turn left (south) on SH16</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex">
                <span class="bg-blue-400 text-white rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold mr-3 mt-1">4</span>
                <span>Follow signs to Kaukapakapa village</span>
              </li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Travel Tips for Wainui Clients</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>• Perfect time to let hair air-dry naturally during the drive</li>
            <li>• Morning appointments offer peaceful rural drive</li>
            <li>• Combine with Kumeu wine region visits (additional 15 minutes)</li>
            <li>• Scenic country drive helps you relax before treatment</li>
            <li>• Return journey timing perfect for sunset village walks</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials from Wainui Clients -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">What Wainui Village Residents Say</h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
            <div class="flex mb-4">
              {[...Array(5)].map((_, i) => (
                <svg key={i} class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-500 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon>
                </svg>
              ))}
            </div>
