              "Living an active village lifestyle, I was struggling with environmental damage and sun exposure. Melissa's keratin treatment and UV protection regimen have completely transformed my hair. It looks healthy and feels amazing, even after my most active days!"
            </p>
            <p class="font-medium">- Jake M., Wainui Resident</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
            <div class="flex mb-4">
              {[...Array(5)].map((_, i) => (
                <svg key={i} class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-500 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon>
                </svg>
              ))}
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-4">
              "Living at Wainui means enjoying fresh air and outdoor activities. Hair By Melissa understands village living like no other salon I've tried. My balayage looks naturally sun-kissed and requires minimal maintenance - perfect for village life!"
