  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions - Wainui</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Where is the closest hair salon to Wainui?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Hair By Melissa in Kaukapakapa is the closest professional hair salon to Wainui, located just 20 minutes away via Wainui Road and SH16. We specialize in hair care for village living and understand the unique needs of Wainui's rural community.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Do you understand village hair care for Wainui residents?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Absolutely! We specialize in hair care for village living. Our treatments are designed to protect against environmental factors, UV damage, and humidity - perfect for Wainui's rural lifestyle. Our keratin treatments are particularly popular with active village residents.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
